    <h2 {...{
      "id": "configuring-tests-for-native-vs-hybrid-apps"
    }}>{`Configuring Tests for Native vs. Hybrid Apps`}</h2>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`iPhone 6 Real Device`}</strong></p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`{
deviceName:'iPhone 6 Device',
platformName:'iOS',
platformVersion:'8.4',
app:'sauce-storage:SampleIOSApp.ipa',
"appium-version":"1.4.16"
